calafia home page header about calafia the california cooperative latin american collection development group better known as calafia is a consortium of california libraries calafia enjoys the support and strength of the libraries at stanford university the university of california system and the university of southern california the combined latin american holdings of the calafia group number more than one million volumes and are surpassed only by the library of congress latin american studies collection affiliated organizations alzar lamp lane lanic larrp laser mollas salalm
